SCHEMA: system/failure_event.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.system.failure_event
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Declare canonical system-level failure events for SYS-6 reliability outputs.

NON-SEMANTICS:
- No implicit failure generation outside deterministic process paths.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record failure_event
  required:
    - event_id: id
    - system_id: id
    - failure_mode_id: id
    - tick: int
    - deterministic_fingerprint: text
    - extensions: map
